{"tid":394172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"依個世界你越正義就死得越快，不如做一個仆街","createTime":"2017-09-09T17:21:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-10T03:51:09.000Z","uid":80178,"like":22,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"983d26ca64bbef1187427ca46ef4e232cd533045","tid":394172,"uid":80178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T17:21:13.000Z","msg":"曾經你覺得依個世界好唔公平<br />\n曾經你覺得社會上既統治者係一班人渣<br />\n你好想反抗<br />\n你好想要一個更公義既社會<br />\n但係你人微言輕<br />\n你越反抗人地就越打壓你<br />\n你好唔甘心<br />\n點解你為個社會付出咁多精力甚至你既前途<br />\n個社會都一成不變<br />\n而果d能力不如你既自私仆街<br />\n就因為專注事業同擦鞋而一世騎住你<br />\n你越黎越憤怒<br />\n越黎越憎恨依個人生<br />\n係依個咁病態既社會<br />\n要活得快樂就只可以做一個自顧自己既仆街仔"},{"pid":"1e537b5597a6ff7b45db01c60fe9c4e6511cf070","tid":394172,"uid":133727,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T17:22:09.000Z","msg":"已閱"},{"pid":"a57265eb3d1b6ae1833cb7e9a3c9013604beae37","tid":394172,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T17:22:11.000Z","msg":"是"},{"pid":"66cbf297bb0309ab5dbf390b350bcf7841e2be6b","tid":394172,"uid":54876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T17:22:59.000Z","msg":"仆唔仆街都可以顧掂自己<br />\n應該咁講，顧掂自己先再講正唔正義"},{"pid":"8d6bc5e510d2d73c1edf2c005e73e8f6a0c3eaa3","tid":394172,"uid":79735,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T17:24:28.000Z","msg":"點解咁怕死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟做個對得住良心嘅短命種好<br />\n定<br />\n做個無惡不作而長命不歲嘅賤人好"},{"pid":"4aeecaee6faf0f5b6174005d5f31120afe8bde8f","tid":394172,"uid":49935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T17:32:36.000Z","msg":"條命生成咁仲可以點 有時真係唔到你唔認命<br />\n做好人永遠都係蝕底 人善比人欺<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2ff593e037f741eee41af4f577e81825fb95b21","tid":394172,"uid":49004,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T17:42:16.000Z","msg":"以前古人為仕節而死<br />\n死後都可以搏史書一讚<br />\n<br />\n宜家球證旁證足協全部都係共狗嘅人<br />\n死左仲會數臭你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1820a1729bcced9671337a3daaec3d092afd43d9","tid":394172,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T17:44:59.000Z","msg":"開得呢個po證明你仲有良知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f41330211598c6780c200f76738d3804a0bbb5d0","tid":394172,"uid":86249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T18:53:43.000Z","msg":"殺人放火金腰帶千古定律"},{"pid":"58440be5fee34ea42644b1e5e01e555810da73aa","tid":394172,"uid":93655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T18:56:19.000Z","msg":"香港人！識醒未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6feaf0f6bd06d7f772611eecc4bfb9a2f9f75271","tid":394172,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T19:06:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>曾經你覺得依個世界好唔公平<br />\n曾經你覺得社會上既統治者係一班人渣<br />\n你好想反抗<br />\n你好想要一個更公義既社會<br />\n但係你人微言輕<br />\n你越反抗人地就越打壓你<br />\n你好唔甘心<br />\n點解你為個社會付出咁多精力甚至你既前途<br />\n個社會都一成不變<br />\n而果d能力不如你既自私仆街<br />\n就因為專注事業同擦鞋而一世騎住你<br />\n你越黎越憤怒<br />\n越黎越憎恨依個人生<br />\n係依個咁病態既社會<br />\n要活得快樂就只可以做一個自顧自己既仆街仔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蠢同正義係兩回事"},{"pid":"b58b0ab7b5f096c4c801e534555e7ec7c05bc864","tid":394172,"uid":104443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T19:07:59.000Z","msg":"一個名留千古，一個遺臭萬年，樓主肯定想做後者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27dc1e44a1d41f248bc0986cce06b553945ddd64","tid":394172,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T19:40:27.000Z","msg":"悶唔悶"},{"pid":"2a756e438ec2f2af75bf91d3de9ec112157701d0","tid":394172,"uid":35106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T20:03:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個名留千古，一個遺臭萬年，樓主肯定想做後者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n名留千古..<br />\n而今香港過多一年咪又係忘記你"},{"pid":"812f8e29869ca80bd25b078e3d83bd74d